-   $\sigma_1$ (Sigma_1): Cavitation index equal to $(P_2 - P_v)/\Delta{P} = (\sigma - 1)$ at service conditions;
-   $\sigma_2$ (Sigma_2): Cavitation index equal to $(P_2 - P_v)/(\Delta{P}+v^2/2g)$ at service conditions.

